track_notes: This is a familly walk, the place is very nice, if you walk counter clockwise, you can leave the familly at the lakes while you go to the summit for radio. Plenty room for antenna, the sight is wonderfull. You can park the car at the Parking for free.

This is a nice walk not too long not difficult.
The panorama is wonderfull Nice place for radio too!

This trac is anticlockwise to reach 2 summits. Not too difficult, not too long, therefore you must have good health, good shoes and lot of water in hot wx. Also take some rain clothes, because it is hight mountains, the landscape is wonderfull, plenty room to park and for antenna.
Up and down, this path will leads you to some nice lakes
Walking up to the lac den veillos

This is the shorter path to summit, you can use it up&down even in winter time with ski or snow-shoes.
